      %h1 Meetups
      %p Our meetups are open to all experience levels, from total novices to expert Rubyists. Do come along!

      .vevent
        %h2.summary An Introduction to Ruby

        %h3.when-icon.icon When?
        %p
          %span.dtstart
            - date_string = '2014-02-04'
            - date = Date.parse date_string
            %abbr.value{ :title => "#{date_string}" } #{date.strftime("#{date.day.ordinalize} %B, %Y")}
            %span.value 6:30pm

        %h3.where-icon.icon
          Where?
          %a.get-directions{ :href => "http://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&source=s_d&saddr=&hl=en&ie=UTF8&layer=c&daddr=The%20Rumble%20Laboratory%20@54.60231963589608,-5.927209854125977", :title => "The Rumble Laboratory"} Get Directions

        %p.location
          The Rumble Laboratory
          %br
          2nd Floor, 46 Hill Street, Belfast, BT1 2LB

        %h3.what-icon.icon What?
        %p.description
          For our first Belfast Ruby meetup of 2014 weâ€™ll be holding a few short talks focused on making the jump to Ruby, open to people of all experience levels.
